About Tunnel Rush

Tunnel Rush is an endless runner-style video game in which players control a character navigating through a tunnel while avoiding obstacles. The game features fast-paced action and a colorful, neon-lit aesthetic. Players can collect coins and power-ups to help them progress further in the game, and can also unlock new characters and tunnels to play in. 

The game's goal is to survive as long as possible while collecting coins and power-ups, and avoiding obstacles such as walls and barriers. The game increases its speed as the player progresses, making it more challenging.
